      <container name="Recalling" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Recalling</span> Articles 8, 97 and 100 of the Charter of the United Nations,</p>
      </container>
      <container name="Recalling also" eId="container_3">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Recalling also</span> Article 101 of the Charter, which governs the appointment, employment and recruitment of staff,</p>
      </container>
      <container name="Recalling further" eId="container_4">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Recalling further</span> its resolutions <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/42/220">42/220</a> A of 21 December 1987, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/49/222">49/222</a> A of 23 December 1994, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/49/222b">49/222</a> B of 20 July 1995, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/51/226">51/226</a> of 3 April 1997, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/52/219">52/219</a> of 22 December 1997, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/53/221">53/221</a> of 7 April 1999, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/55/258">55/258</a> of 14 June 2001, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/57/305">57/305</a> of 15 April 2003, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/59/266">59/266</a> of 23 December 2004, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/59/287">59/287</a> of 13 April 2005, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/60/1">60/1</a> of 16 September 2005, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/60/238">60/238</a> of 23 December 2005, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/60/254">60/254</a> of 8 May 2006, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/60/260">60/260</a> of 8 May 2006, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/61/244">61/244</a> of 22 December 2006, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/62/247">62/247</a> of 3 April 2008, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/63/250">63/250</a> of 24 December 2008, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/65/247">65/247</a> of 24 December 2010, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/66/234">66/234</a> of 24 December 2011, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/67/255">67/255</a> of 12 April 2013, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/68/252">68/252</a> of 27 December 2013, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/68/265">68/265</a> of 9 April 2014, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/70/244">70/244</a> of 23 December 2015, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/71/263">71/263</a> of 23 December 2016 and <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/77/278">77/278</a> of 18 April 2023 as well as its other relevant resolutions and decisions,</p>
